<p>Seems like you’ve misunderstood what multiple classes/functions/parameters do; here is the case that’s likely causing the tests to fail. EncoderSim is for quadrature encoders connected to the RoboRIO DIO and read using the Encoder class; the “index” mentioned is a HAL index used by the native HAL code and shouldn’t be used from team code (the similar <code>createForChannel</code> factory method accepts a DIO channel number).</p>
<p>Encoders connected to <span class="abbreviation">CTRE<template class="tooltiptext" data-text="Cross The Road Electronics"></template></span> (or other) <span class="abbreviation">CAN<template class="tooltiptext" data-text="Controller Area Network"></template></span> devices are a whole other story, and use the relevant vendor’s simulation stuff. I recommend reading up on <span class="abbreviation">CTRE<template class="tooltiptext" data-text="Cross The Road Electronics"></template></span>’s SimCollection docs, in your case.</p>","post_number":10,"post_type":1,"posts_count":16,"updated_at":"2022-12-31T23:08:47.373Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":9,"quote_count":1,"incoming_link_count":2,"reads":99,"readers_count":98,"score":34.8,"yours":false,"topic_id":420424,"topic_slug":"frc-swerve-module-simulation-ci-test-need-help-simulating-while-testing","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":45763,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"user_custom_fields":{"user_field_4":"6738a | ISR | WPILib"},"post_url":"/t/frc-swerve-module-simulation-ci-test-need-help-simulating-while-testing/420424/10","custom_user_title":"6738a | ISR | WPILib","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3115079,"name":"","username":"a1cd","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/a1cd/{size}/179304_2.png","created_at":"2023-01-01T00:21:15.284Z","cooked":"